11 12 13
[THEN] 14 -> 14 }T

T{ [ELSE] -1 [IF] 15 [ELSE] 16 [THEN] 17 [THEN] 18 -> 18 }T

\ A lone [THEN] is a noop
T{ 19 [THEN] 20 -> 19 20 }T

